snippet.title: Catacomb Abyss 3D gameplay (PC Game, 1992)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Catacomb Abyss 3D, Dos PC game produced by Softdisk Publishing in 1992 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/catacomb-abyss-3d/5054/
I explored the first few areas of this slightly confusing RPG/shooter hybrid .
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
Nitemare 3D - https://youtu.be/n7Q0QlADCyw
